fileimporter-specialpage: Title for the File Import special page.
fileimporter-cantparseurl: Error message shown on the special page when the URL entered can not be parsed.
fileimporter-cantimporturl: Error message shown on the special page when the URL entered can not be imported from.
fileimporter-exampleprefix:
Prefix for the example URL contained within the URL text box on the special page.
{{Identical|Example}}
fileimporter-textrevisionsprefix: Prefix for the number of text revisions to be imported on the special page.
fileimporter-filerevisionsprefix: Prefix for the number of file revisions to be imported on the special page.
fileimporter-titleprefix: Prefix for the title to be imported on the special page.
fileimporter-submit:
Text for the submit button on the special page.
{{Identical|Submit}}
fileimporter-import:
Text for the import button on the special page.
{{Identical|Import}}
fileimporter-importfilefromprefix: Prefix for the URL being imported from on the special page.
